quran[4{c,v,t}:
33,51,( aur tum ko yeh bhi ikhtiyar hai ke ) jis biwi ko chaho alehda rakho aur jisay chaho apne paas rakho. aur jis ko tum ne alehda kardiya ho agar is ko phir apne paas talab karlo to tum par kuch gunah nahi. yeh ( ijazat ) is liye hai ke un ki ankhen thandhi rahen aur woh ghumnaak nah hon aur jo kuch tum un ko do. usay le kar sab khush rahen. aur jo kuch tumahray dilon mein hai khuda usay jaanta hai. aur khuda jan-nay wala aur Burdbar hai
33,52,( ae paighambar ) un ke siwa aur aurtain tum ko jaaiz nahi aur nah yeh ke un biwion ko chore kar aur biwiyan karo khuwa un ka husn tum ko ( kaisa hi ) acha lagey magar woh jo tumahray haath ka maal hai ( yani londion ke baray mein tum ko ikhtiyar hai ) aur khuda har cheez par nigah rakhta hai
33,53,momino paighambar ke gharon mein nah jaya karo magar is soorat mein ke tum ko khanay ke liye ijazat di jaye aur is ke paknay ka intzaar bhi nah karna parre. lekin jab tumhari dawat ki jaye to jao aur jab khana کھاچکو to chal do aur baton mein jee laga kar nah baith raho. yeh baat paighambar ko aeza deti hai. aur woh tum se sharam karte hain ( aur kehte nahi hain ) lekin khuda sachhi baat ke kehnay se sharam nahi karta. aur jab payghambaroon ki biwion se koi samaan mango to parday ke bahar mango. yeh tumahray aur un ke dono ke dilon ke liye bohat pakizgee ki baat hai. aur tum ko yeh Shayaan nahi ke paighambar khuda ko takleef do aur nah yeh ke un ki biwion se kabhi un ke baad nikah karo. be shak yeh khuda ke nazdeek bara ( gunah ka kaam ) hai
33,54,agar tum kisi cheez ko zahir karo ya is ko makhfi rakho to ( yaad rakho ke ) khuda har cheez se bakhabar hai
